Package: mbadtools
Title: MBAD Data Analytics Functions
Version: 0.0.2.0001
Authors@R: 
    person("Bruce", "Hartman", , "bruce@ahartman.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Some functions useful for my MBAD courses on Data Analytics. 
    Loads packages from core packages list on library call
    Includes Residual plots, Pareto plots, and adding significance color to pvalues in a gt table.
    Includes Granger causality table and plot functions.
    Includes functions for handling VAR models with bvartools and plotting.
